WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:04.000
Hands place a package on the table, carefully.

00:04.000 --> 00:08.000
The white label reflects the light as fingers smooth it out.

00:08.000 --> 00:12.000
The sound of paper and tape breaks the silence of the room.

00:12.000 --> 00:16.000
The edges separate calmly, revealing what's inside.

00:16.000 --> 00:18.000
A simple moment, full of contained curiosity.
